me.hyperperform.reporting

Interface IReport

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ReportGenerator

    public interface IReport
    Serves as the Context in strategy design pattern. Each report generator is has an Algorithm. Provides a common interface for all report generators, this allows for consistency. Contains three contracts to be met by any realization.
    Since:
    : 2016/08/18
    Version:
    : 1.0
    Author:
